                <div class="spacer-huge card-spacer"></div>
                <div class="card-text-wrapper">
                  <div class="heading-style-h5">Tables</div>
                  <div class="text-style-muted">Build custom schemas to work with structured data inside of Composer.</div>
                </div><img src="/webflow/images/Tables-grid-card-bkg-no-border.png" loading="lazy" alt="A snapshot of DXOS tables with custom schema" class="tables-grid-card-bkg">
              </div>
              <div id="w-node-_41002e10-b86a-cbf8-2679-4685cb45b6db-cb45b6a7" class="dxos_stack-card sheets">
                <div class="spacer-huge card-spacer"></div>
                <div class="card-text-wrapper">
                  <div class="heading-style-h5">Sheets</div>
                  <div class="text-style-muted">Leverage a local-first spreadsheet that supports custom functions.</div>
                </div><img src="/webflow/images/sheets-grid-card-bkg-no-border.png" loading="lazy" alt="A snapshot of DXOS sheets with custom functions" class="sheets-grid-card-bkg">
              </div>
              <div id="w-node-_41002e10-b86a-cbf8-2679-4685cb45b6e3-cb45b6a7" class="dxos_stack-card sketch">
                <div class="spacer-huge"></div>
                <div class="card-text-wrapper">
                  <div class="heading-style-h5">Sketches</div>
                  <div class="text-style-muted">Embed diagrams and sketches to include them in your programatic workflows.</div>
                </div><img src="/webflow/images/Sketches-bkg-grid-card-no-border.png" loading="lazy" alt="Snapshot of a TLDraw canvas inside of Composer by DXOS" class="sketches-bkg-grid-card">
              </div>
              <div id="w-node-_41002e10-b86a-cbf8-2679-4685cb45b6eb-cb45b6a7" class="horizontal-line-wrap">
                <div class="horiozontal-line"></div>
              </div>
              <div id="w-node-_41002e10-b86a-cbf8-2679-4685cb45b6ed-cb45b6a7" class="dxos_stack-card short">
                <div class="card-text-wrapper">
                  <div class="dxos_stack-label">
                    <div>Coming Soon</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="heading-style-h5">Custom Functions</div>
                  <div class="text-style-muted">Deploy custom functions that allow you to leverage data from any source and build programatic workflows inside of Composer.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="grid-corner-float"><img src="/webflow/images/Custom-Functions.png" loading="lazy" alt=""></div>
              </div>
