                        <div class="text-size-large text-style-muted balanced">Leave the cloud behind and collaborate peer to peer on any supported data type</div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="circles-tab-pane-wrap w-tab-pane">
